      "role": "user",
      "content": "elven dance? lol okay. what about the actual chemistry though? like what is the specific breakdown of the molecules involved? i need to be able to write this down in scientific terms for my exam, not just talk about magic. can u give me a more technical breakdown of the intermediate compounds?",
